source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_SEQ_00<tab>Anogg won't be kept from the secrets of the ruins a moment longer.

TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_SEQ_01<tab>You speak with Anogg, who rushes off to chase the “key” that 2P bade you recover before you can get so much as a word in edgeways. At this point, there is little for you or Konogg to do but follow.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_SEQ_01<tab>Anogg est retournée dans les ruines. Rejoignez-la.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_SEQ_02<tab>Catching up to Anogg deeper within the ruins, Konogg attempts to dissuade her from rushing headlong into danger at 2P's behest, making the rather astute observation that you hardly know her and you definitely do <var 1A 02 /var>not<var 1A 01 /var> know her true intentions. Anogg, however, refuses to consider that he may have a point, and insists upon cooperation with the android, believing it to be the most expedient means of making even greater discoveries. It seems that you have no choice but to pick a side.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_SEQ_02<tab>Suite à un léger désaccord, les jumeaux ont décidé de poursuivre l'exploration des ruines séparément. Choisissez lequel des deux vous souhaitez accompagner, selon votre tendance à la réserve ou votre goût de l'adversité.
TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_001<tab>Ayé, vous êtes <var 08 E905 ((prête)) ((prêt)) /var><var 1D /var>? J'en ai assez d'attendre, on y retourne<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_KONOGG_000_005<tab>There's no stopping her now. So much for preparation.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_KONOGG_000_005<tab>Quand Anogg a une idée en tête, rien ne peut l'en détourner. Mieux vaut se taire et la laisser faire comme ça lui chante.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_050<tab>Just think─machines equal to man! No, perhaps even greater! If we can find the key, we can figure out how they work! We can fix 2P, and then...
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_050<tab>N'empêche, quelles merveilles, ces androïdes... Ils n'ont rien à envier aux humains, ce serait même plutôt l'inverse.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_KONOGG_000_051<tab>...And what? Slow down and use your head! How are we to know that any of what she said was true?
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_KONOGG_000_051<tab>Dis donc, Anogg, ça te dérangerait d'être un peu plus prudente<var 1D /var>? À avancer sans réfléchir, on va finir par s'attirer des ennuis...

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_052<tab>Oh, so you'd have us sit on our hands instead of pursuing the untold power that sleeps in these ruins? Twiddle our thumbs while others race ahead and claim the prize?
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_052<tab>Comment ça, plus prudente<var 1D /var>? Dis tout de suite que tu veux rentrer au village, pendant que tu y es<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_KONOGG_000_053<tab>I'm as intrigued as you are! But I would <var 1A 02 /var>not<var 1A 01 /var> have us put our blind faith in someone we've only just met─particularly someone making such wild claims. Were we to bring this “key” to her, there's no telling what she might do with it...
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_KONOGG_000_053<tab>Qui a parlé de rentrer au village<var 1D /var>? Je dis simplement qu'on ne devrait pas faire une confiance aveugle à 2P. Rien ne garantit qu'elle nous ait raconté la vérité.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_054<tab>Hmph. If you want to be a coward, be my guest. I'll be boldly forging a path forward as, if you recall, we planned to do. And if we can secure 2P's continued assistance, all the better.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_054<tab>Écoute... Si t'es pas content, t'as qu'à explorer les ruines de ton côté.

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_055<tab>What about you? You can either dive into the great unknown with me, or stick in one toe at a time like a beardless baby.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_ANOGG_000_055<tab>Quant à vous, vous pouvez nous suivre l'un ou l'autre, ça n'a pas d'importance. Allez-y, choisissez, on ne va pas y passer la journée<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_KONOGG_000_060<tab>Sometimes I hate being the reasonable one.
target: TEXT_LUCKTA003_03719_KONOGG_000_060<tab>Anogg est parfois tellement à bloc qu'elle est incapable de prendre du recul sur la situation. C'est pas facile pour moi...
